blog.name: amalasdraws
blog.title: I wear my scars like the rings on a pimp

body:
For creators

This is just a small suggestion. Take it or leave it.

If you post your creations online try to stay away from phrases like “this is shit”, “here is my trash” and equally down putting words. I get where you are coming from. It’s from a place of insecurity. If you put it down from the beginning you won’t be disappointed when others don’t like it.

The thing is you are insulting those who do like it. Make them feel they have bad taste for liking your “trash”. It also makes people to not care. Why should they if you don’t even care?!

It’s totally valid to not always be satisfied with your work. And you can absolutely voice frustration, even in a content post. But try to keep it more constructive.

You will see it helps you and your work!

summary: IT HAS BEGUN! I am taking commissions this summer peeps. I’ll be taking 6 slots only. DA RULES:  Communicate with me with your...
caption:
IT HAS BEGUN!

I am taking commissions this summer peeps. I’ll be taking 6 slots only.

DA RULES:

  1.  Communicate with me with your commission request to my email: n15rodriguez@yahoo.com
  2. Please be sure to include your email/username in the e-mail.
  3. All payments will be made by PAYPAL. Be sure your payment includes your username and “COMMISSION”.
  4. Commission sketches will be done before payment for approval.
  5. Commissions will be completed and sent to you ONLY after payment is made.

DA GUIDELINES:

  1. I will NOT draw full-on nudity or pornograhic images depicting sexual interaction (nipples and bare backsides do not fall under this rule. Basically no genitalia or sex related acts)
  2. I will NOT draw anything related to religion, politics, occultism, or things in poor tatse. (I’m not interested in drawings things of that serious stature)
  3. I will NOT draw graphic violence or gore (blood and such does not fall under this rule)
  4. I will NOT draw any of the related subjects:
  • Pregnancy
  • Vore
  • Inflation
  • Scat
  • Other bodily functions
  • Extreme lactation
  • Anything else I’ll mention should it be brought up to me

Again i will not take your commission, if you don’t follow the guideline have typed here.

Other then that I await your Commish Request.
